1. *Osobu* obično upoznajemo preko prijatelja. (We usually get to know a person through friends.)
2. Ona je *osobu* upoznala na sajmu knjiga. (She met the person at a book fair.)
3. Ona se odrekla udobnosti da bi pomogla *osobi*. (She gave up comfort to help the person.)
4. Ovaj čovek je poznat po tome što je pomogao mnogim *osobama*. (This man is known for helping many people.)
5. *Osoba* koja je postigla uspeh u svojoj profesiji je uzor mnogim ljudima. (The person who achieved success in their profession is an example for many people.)